        Vessel (MSV)s, and 1 Expeditionary Fast Transport (EPF) (formerly JHSV), providing up to 300 imagery and other payload
        hours, per month for a total of 18,000 hours per year for afloat commanders lacking organic tactical ISR capability. (Baseline:
